item.description:
Come join us for a fun day of disc golf. Don't worry if you can't throw a frisbee well. We'll just have fun. All you need to do is toss it at the metal baskets along the wooded course. We have lots of fun and laughs so please join us.

You can pick up a disc at the store where we meet. No Charge.
Here's a link to to the park.
http://www.pelhamweb.....

Bring bug spray, sunscreen, good shoes, water and a friend.

My # is 315-0275 if you need more info.

If it rains we can move the date to sunday.

Cindy
item.how_to_find_us: We will meet at the store across from the park
item.name: Wimp Disc Golf
